    <mxCell id="jnote" value="The jacket is modelled as a &lt;b&gt;single lumped temperature T&lt;sub&gt;c&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&#10;The paper defines no coolant flow rate and no separate&#10;jacket inlet/outlet, so no flow direction is implied." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#c0392b;strokeColor=#e8c4bf;fillColor=#fdf3f2;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
