    <mxCell id="eqn" value="&#7819;&#8321; = &#8722;x&#8321; + Da(1&#8722;x&#8321;)&#8319; exp[x&#8322;/(1+x&#8322;/&#947;)]&#10;&#7819;&#8322; = &#8722;x&#8322; + B&#183;Da(1&#8722;x&#8321;)&#8319; exp[x&#8322;/(1+x&#8322;/&#947;)] &#8722; &#946;(x&#8322; &#8722; x&lt;sub&gt;2c&lt;/sub&gt;) + &#946;u + d&#10;x&#8321; = (c&lt;sub&gt;af&lt;/sub&gt; &#8722; c&lt;sub&gt;a&lt;/sub&gt;)/c&lt;sub&gt;af&lt;/sub&gt; &#160;(conversion)&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;x&#8322; = &#947;(T &#8722; T&lt;sub&gt;f0&lt;/sub&gt;)/T&lt;sub&gt;f0&lt;/sub&gt; &#160;(temperature)&#10;&#946; = hA/(F&#961;c&lt;sub&gt;p&lt;/sub&gt;)&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;Da = k&#8320;Ve&lt;sup&gt;&#8722;&#947;&lt;/sup&gt;/F&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#947; = E/(RT&lt;sub&gt;f0&lt;/sub&gt;)&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;B = (&#8722;&#916;H)c&lt;sub&gt;af&lt;/sub&gt;&#947;/(&#961;c&lt;sub&gt;p&lt;/sub&gt;T&lt;sub&gt;f0&lt;/sub&gt;)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;fontColor=#333333;strokeColor=#cccccc;fillColor=#f7f7f7;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="100" y="640" width="700" height="92" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

    <mxCell id="caveat" value="The paper works entirely in &lt;b&gt;dimensionless variables&lt;/b&gt; and assigns no units to F, c&lt;sub&gt;af&lt;/sub&gt;, V, T, A or h; none are printed here.&#10;It gives no numerical parameter values and contains no process schematic &#8212; this diagram is composed from its text and nomenclature." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;fontColor=#777777;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=4;" vertex="1" parent="1">
